  {name: "★ COURS DE BACHATA avec YOANN & NADÈGE - BACHATACCRO ★", description: "Vous voulez apprendre à danser la Bachata ?\r\nOu même progresser et/ou vous perfectionner ?\r\n\r\nQuelque soit votre âge, que vous soyez seul(e) ou en couple,\r\nCes cours sont faits pour vous !\r\n\r\n\r\nYoann & Nadège, professeurs internationaux,  dispensent des cours réguliers de Bachata tous les mardis soirs.\r\n\r\nProfitez de cours de Bachata \"Mix style\", mélange des différents styles de Bachata pour donner plus de vie à la danse.\r\nModerna, Dominican, Sensual, Fusion, ... il y en aura pour tous les goûts.\r\n\r\nFaites la différence par votre style !\r\n\r\n\r\nYoann et Nadège sont des professeurs reconnus et pédagogues, plusieurs fois champions de Bachata en France et en Belgique, 10ème meilleurs danseurs d'Europe.\r\n\r\nIls vous assurerons des cours dynamiques et de qualité !\r\n\r\n\r\nApprenez et évoluez à votre rythme, dans la convivialité et la bonne humeur.\r\n\r\n\r\n_____LES COURS______\r\n\r\n\r\nTous les MARDIS\r\n\r\n(hors vacances scolaires et jours fériés)\r\n\r\n\r\n# 20h30 - Cours \"débutants/débutants +\"\r\n\r\n# 21h30 - Cours \"intermédiaires/avancés\" \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nATTENTION, tous les cours commencent à l'heure !\r\n\r\n\r\nInscriptions acceptées durant toute l'année, plusieurs formules proposées.\r\nLes inscriptions doivent se faire avant le début du cours.\r\n\r\n\r\nATTENTION, merci de venir avec des chaussures propres pour les cours de danse.\r\n\r\nVestiaire à disposition.\r\n\r\n\r\n______LIEUX______\r\n\r\nStudio de danse\r\n20 rue Marceau\r\n92170 VANVES\r\n\r\nSous-sol de l'école Marceau\r\n\r\nInterphone : \"danse\"\r\n\r\n\r\n________ACCÈS________\r\n\r\n\r\nMétro ligne 13 : Malakoff - Plateau de Vanves\r\n\r\n\r\nBus : 58 - 89\r\n\r\nVélib' et Autolib' \r\n\r\nPlaces de stationnement libre\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n______INFOS, TARIFS & INSCRIPTIONS_______\r\n\r\n\r\nwww.bachataccro.e-monsite.com\r\n\r\nbachataccro@hotmail.fr\r\n06.61.18.02.05 ou 06.67.44.64.05\r\n\r\nPlan :\r\nhttp://bachataccro.e-monsite.com/pages/salles-de-danse.html\r\n\r\nTarifs & bulletins d'insscription :\r\nhttp://bachataccro.e-monsite.com/pages/tarifs.html\r\n\r\n_______________________________________\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nVENEZ NOMBREUX, REPARTEZ HEUREUX !\r\n\r\n\r\n_______________________________________\r\n\r\n\r\nNous suivre ?!\r\n\r\n\r\nSITE WEB\r\nNotre site : www.bachataccro.e-monsite.com\r\n\r\nFACEBOOK\r\n_Profil : https://www.facebook.com/bachataccro\r\n_Groupe : https://www.facebook.com/groups/125951650832959/\r\n_Page : https://www.facebook.com/pages/Yoann-El-rom%C3%A1ntico-Nad%C3%A8ge-La-leona-Bachataccro/304049782962188\r\n\r\nTWITTER\r\nTweets : https://twitter.com/BACHATACCRO\r\n\r\nYOUTUBE\r\nChaîne : http://www.youtube.com/user/SalsaBachatera\r\n\r\n\r\n*****Un évènement BACHATACCRO*****", start_time: "2015-09-15 18:20:00", end_time: "2016-01-12 21:30:00", eid: "1628947034017542", picture: "https://fbcdn-photos-d-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-xpt1/v/t1.0-0/p180x540/11406996_731684673607430_6051334192989976367_n.jpg?oh=4f35d0ad8da542e382b07a03ccc01d89&oe=566C1B07&__gda__=1449107233_ce8b4f248fc97fe2ec7d2a03c4e91ea8", image: "11406996_731684673607430_6051334192989976367_n.jpg", venue: " ", location: "Studio de danse\r\n20 rue Marceau\r\n92170\r\n", city: "Paris", country: nil, country_code: "FR", longitude: "2.2953299", latitude: "48.824357", website: "", sandbox: false, timezone: nil, slug: "cours-de-bachata-avec-yoann-nadege-bachataccro", event_type_id: 1, owner_fb_id: "743081655801065", sale_notification_email: nil},
  {name: "O'DANCE  FIESTA BRUSSELS", description: "EVERY WEDNESDAY @ O’DANCE FIESTA\r\n\r\nSALSA MEETS KIZOMBA, ZOUK & MORE WITH O'DANCE FIESTA : TWO DANCE FLOORS FOR TWICE AS MUCH DANCE PLEASURE !!!! DANCERS FROM 21H30 : ONLY 5 € !!!! A UNIQUE VENUE IN BRUSSELS WHERE SALSA LOVERS & KIZOMBA/ZOUK DANCERS CAN PERFECT THEIR SKILLS (CLASSES) OR DANCE THE NIGHT AWAY !!!\r\n\r\nA PROMISE FOR A TREMENDOUS EVENING ...... JUST IMAGINE THE SENSUAL KIZOMBA DANCERS MINGLING WITH THE ALLURING ZOUK, BACHATA DANCERS ... WHAT A DELIGHT FOR THE EYES !!! AND OF COURSE, OUR SALSA AFICIONADOS WHOOSHING ACROSS THE DANCE FLOOR LIKE STARS IN THE SKY !!! WHAT A PROGRAMME !!!!\r\n\r\nU WANT TO BE PART OF IT ? DOORS OPEN TO THE TEMPLE OF O'DANCE FIESTA  FROM 19 :00 ONWARDS !!! ENJOY !!!\r\n\r\n__________________________________________________________\r\nRENCONTRE ENTRE LA SALSA & LE KIZOMBA, BACHATA ZOUK & MORE, O'DANCE FIESTA : DEUX PISTES DE DANSE POUR DEUX FOIS PLUS DE PLAISIR !!! A PARTIR DE 21H30 : 5€ SEULEMENT !!! UNE GRANDE PREMIERE A BRUXELLES, UN ENDROIT OU LES AFICIONADOS DE LA SALSA & LES DANSEURS DE KIZOMBA, BACHATA ZOUK PEUVENT SUIVRE DES COURS OU DANSER JUSQU'AU BOUT DE LA NUIT !!!!\r\n\r\nLA PROMESSE D'UNE SOIREE TORRIDE …… IMAGINEZ DONC LA SENSUALITE DES DANSEURS DE KIZOMBA MELANGE AU RAVISSEMENT DES DANSEURS DE BACHATA…. QUEL PLAISIR POUR LES SENS !!!! ET PUIS, BIEN EVIDEMMENT NOS AMIS SALSEROS DEFERLANT SUR LA PISTE AVEC GRACE ET STYLE !!! QUEL PROGRAMME LES AMIS !!!\r\n\r\n\r\nALORS, INTERESSE ? LES PORTES DU TEMPLE DE LA O'DANCE FIESTA  OUVRENT A 19:00", start_time: "2015-09-16 17:00:00", end_time: "2015-12-09 00:05:00", eid: "1599457163673296", picture: "https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xft1/v/t1.0-9/s720x720/11012107_837814839637818_4087288731061228659_n.jpg?oh=f373646a45be727e0b77642aadcf7814&oe=5672A2D6", image: "11012107_837814839637818_4087288731061228659_n.jpg", venue: "", location: "Rue Felix Hap,11 - 1040 Etterbeek ", city: "", country: "Azerbaidjan", country_code: "LU", longitude: nil, latitude: nil, website: "", sandbox: true, timezone: nil, slug: "o-dance-fiesta-brussels", event_type_id: nil, owner_fb_id: "287299704689337", sale_notification_email: nil},
  {name: "PORTES OUVERTES / CMD LUXEMBOURG / MERCREDI 16 SEPTEMBRE", description: "CHANGEMYDANCE Luxembourg présente\n\n\nJOURNÉE PORTES OUVERTE KIZOMBA SEMBA GRATUIT POUR TOUS AVEC DARNELL & MÉLISSA \n\n→ Niveau débutant et intermédiaire (évolutif selon le niveau)\n\n■ 20h30 à 21h30 : Cours (niveau debutant )\n■ 21h30 à 22h30 : Cours (niveau intermédiaire)\n\nSUIVI DE LA SOIRÉE MIXÉ PAR DJ K'RIM\n\n----------------------------------------------\n\nLES COURS ET LA SOIRÉE SONT GRATUIT POUR LA PORTE OUVERTE \n\n★★★ TARIFS HABITUEL ★★★\n\n■ 10€ : le cours \n■ 15€ : les 2 cours\n\n- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -\n\n→ LIEU : LIMBO CLUB : 7 CÔTE D'EICH / LUXEMBOURG VILLE\n\nA bientôt,\n\nCMD Luxembourg", start_time: "2015-09-16 18:30:00", end_time: "2015-12-30 00:00:00", eid: "394157747444677", picture: "https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xpt1/v/t1.0-9/s720x720/11885074_10206506940303700_7169978618079524521_n.jpg?oh=fd4cd10b5d3a7d2941333da587e4630f&oe=56725B5B", image: "11885074_10206506940303700_7169978618079524521_n.jpg", venue: nil, location: "Limbo RestoClub Luxembourg", city: "Luxembourg", country: nil, country_code: "LU", longitude: "6.13135", latitude: "49.6124191", website: nil, sandbox: true, timezone: nil, slug: "portes-ouvertes-cmd-luxembourg-mercredi-16-septembre", event_type_id: nil, owner_fb_id: "10206377578429734", sale_notification_email: nil},
  {name: "Nouveau Atelier chorégraphique K'raib GIRLS", description: "K'raib Dance Academy présente son premier atelier chorégraphique réservé aux filles. \n\nVous souhaitez monter sur scène, réaliser des chorégraphies pendant l'année, vous surpasser, alors cet  atelier est pour vous.\n\nTous les jeudis de 21h45 à 22h45, atelier chorégraphique K'raib Girls avec kenza.\n\nTARIFS \n249 euros pour l'année \n2 ou 3 représentations en France ou à l'étranger.\n\nRenseignements\n07 78 56 18 30", start_time: "2015-09-17 19:45:00", end_time: "2015-09-17 22:45:00", eid: "1646611678956174", picture: "https://fbcdn-photos-g-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-xpf1/t31.0-0/q90/p240x240/11893766_10153656294423689_4544308260670773528_o.jpg", image: "11893766_10153656294423689_4544308260670773528_o.jpg", venue: nil, location: "", city: nil, country: nil, country_code: nil, longitude: nil, latitude: nil, website: nil, sandbox: true, timezone: nil, slug: "nouveau-atelier-choregraphique-k-raib-girls", event_type_id: nil, owner_fb_id: "10153430136512040", sale_notification_email: nil},
  {name: "Zouk Infinity - The Beirut Edition.", description: "NEW DATES & LOWER PRICES…THE BEIRUT ‘RE-EDITION’ – WE LISTENED AND WE ACTED!\r\n\r\nYour opinions as Zoukers & friends mattered and as a result we have listened and have come up with a redefined concept for this fab congress which will make it even better… SO WHAT’S NEW?\r\n\r\n1)\tA CHEAPER CONGRESS PASS – we will now be able to sell passes for £100 GBP. This is half the price of where we were\r\n2)\tWORKSHOPS – Teachers will be giving 3 hours of classes a day\r\n3)\tA UNIQUE VENUE WITH YOUR OWN PRIVATE ISLAND TO DANCE ON - The weather is typically 27 degrees centigrade in September and the party location offers a stunning panoramic view of the Mediterranean\r\n4)\tTWO PARTIES EVERY DAY. We will have a sunset party (from 5-7pm) and then an island party from (10pm to sunrise) every night!\r\n\r\nHow the hell have we done this?\r\n\r\n1)\tWe have managed to secure a cheaper venue that is equally stunning in the beautiful town of Batroun, a major tourist town with the best beaches in Lebanon\r\n2)\tHowever, to secure this venue and cheaper price we had to shift the dates slightly. The congress will now be from the 18th to 21st September with a pre-party on the 17th. \r\n3)\tWe have also exclusively secured the ‘No.1 TripAdvisor’ ranked Pousada in Batroun. Pousada Mayouli gives you cheap rates and the ultimate place to chill when you’re not zouking or exploring; set amongst citrus groves and hammocks. Please note that places are limited at Mayouli!\r\n\r\nWe still have the same amazing DJs CONFIRMED: LIONX (Germany), SOULZ (Poland) and KLEBER (Brazil) \r\n\r\nSo we have a private island, hot weather and parties day & night.  There's less than two months to go so what are you waiting for?\r\n\r\nCheck out the website for more details www.zoukinfinity.com \r\nRegister your place by sending an email to info@zoukinfinity.com", start_time: "2015-09-17 21:00:00", end_time: "2015-09-22 16:00:00", eid: "957861604244948", picture: "https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xfa1/t31.0-8/s720x720/11722403_10152882052257890_6375979424368659822_o.jpg", image: "11722403_10152882052257890_6375979424368659822_o.jpg", venue: "", location: "Beirut, Lebanon", city: "Beirut", country: "", country_code: "LB", longitude: "35.5131", latitude: "33.8869", website: "", sandbox: true, timezone: nil, slug: "zouk-infinity-the-beirut-edition", event_type_id: nil, owner_fb_id: "10153479424907445", sale_notification_email: nil},
  {name: "Free Salsa Music Download on Friday's", description: "RareSalsa.com invites you to a free salsa download every Friday.\n\nJoin this weekly event or our Facebook page to stay up to date and enjoy some wonderful salsa music.\n\nThe Rare Salsa Team \nNYC\nwww.raresalsa.com", start_time: "2015-09-18 00:00:00", end_time: nil, eid: "908109702570557", picture: "https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xtl1/t31.0-8/s720x720/11953490_184520925213360_7796449748475882582_o.jpg", image: "11953490_184520925213360_7796449748475882582_o.jpg", venue: nil, location: "North Pole", city: "Rotterdam", country: nil, country_code: "NL", longitude: "4.67914900532", latitude: "51.7868746749", website: nil, sandbox: true, timezone: nil, slug: "free-salsa-music-download-on-friday-s", event_type_id: nil, owner_fb_id: "185024398496346", sale_notification_email: nil},
  {name: "Mi gente going to Corazon Latino 2015 (Promocode \"SHEMS\")", description: "FESTIVAL CORAZÓN LATINO (Bordeaux) 2015\n\nWith some of the best dancers (and nice people) from whole World…\nAn ideal great place for this kind of events : Le Rocher Palmer\n\nA big Live concert on friday night with TROMBORANGA\n\nA big night show on Saturday night into a place with 650 seats.\n\n5 workshops rooms\n4 rooms for the parties with \n- 1 On1/On2 Salsa \n- 1 Cuban Salsa \n- 1 Kizomba \n- 1 Bachata \n\n2 days of workshops with some of the best teachers and into all levels (50h of workshops) !!! With specials workshops for beginners for who wants to be introduced to new dances.\n\nSalsa (every kind of Salsa), Bachata, Kizomba, Semba, Samba de Gafieira, Lady Styling, Lambazouk…\n\nARTISTS\n\nTROMBORANGA Live\n\nTerry et Cécile (France)\nWilmer y Maria (Cuba/Italy)\nLeon Rose Project (UK/France)  \nMorenasso & Anais (Angola/France)\nRonald & Alba (Colombia/Spain)\nAnderson & Brenda (Brazil)\nFalco B (Ecuador/Spain)\nAlegria DC (France)\nCoco & Fred (Suisse)\nReda (France)\nNuno et Rita (Portugal)\nAlfredo & Andrea - Sabor Dinamico (Colombia/Spain)\nFull Project (Italy)\nCoco & Fred (France/Swiss) \nPedrito & Giusy / Cubaché (Cuba/Italy)\nSelwin & Suleika (Hollande)\nDani K (UK)\nJess (France)\nSam (France)\n\nDJS\nWilly Viper (Paris)\nDiablito (Marseille)\nChad (Paris)\nGass (Paris)\nAmine (Paris)\nSam (Marseille)\nDani K (London)\nM&M’s (Bordeaux)\nAimen (Paris)\n\nONLINE SALE\nwww.weezevent.com/festival-corazon-latino-bordeaux-2015\n\nNeed to know something more ?\nwww.festivalcorazonlatino.com\nrepublicalatina@gmail.com", start_time: "2015-09-18 00:00:00", end_time: nil, eid: "427977117381494", picture: "https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xtf1/v/t1.0-9/s720x720/11407112_10153522621318054_4219930313598235294_n.jpg?oh=a860f47a99f8f308d037cecb7b40d00f&oe=566FD53A", image: "11407112_10153522621318054_4219930313598235294_n.jpg", venue: nil, location: "Bordeaux, France", city: "Bordeaux", country: nil, country_code: "FR", longitude: "-0.5783", latitude: "44.8386", website: nil, sandbox: true, timezone: nil, slug: "mi-gente-going-to-corazon-latino-2015-promocode-shems", event_type_id: nil, owner_fb_id: "10153636568328054", sale_notification_email: nil},
  {name: "Vivir La Vida @ Bayway (Μαρίνα Ζέας)", description: "Και αυτή την Παρασκευή σας περιμένουμε σε έναν μοναδικό χώρο με ατελείωτη πίστα και πανέμορφη θέα, το Bayway Cafe Restaurant Club (Μαρίνα Ζέας).\r\n\r\nΕτοιμαστείτε για πολλά χιλιόμετρα! ;)\r\n\r\nΕΙΣΟΔΟΣ: 10 ευρώ με ποτό\r\nDoors Open: 23:00\r\n\r\nΜια βραδιά που δεν πρέπει να χάσεις!!!\r\nSee Ya All There...\r\n\r\nP.S. Επειδή η λεωφόρος Γρ.Λαμπράκη στον Πειραιά έχει μονοδρομηθεί και δεν μπορείτε να στρίψετε σε αυτή ώστε να βγείτε στην μαρίνα Ζέας, σας προτείνουμε να στρίψετε παρακάτω στην 34ου Συντάγματος\r\n(η οποία στην συνέχειά της λέγεται Λ.Ηρ.Πολυτεχνείου)\r\nη οποία θα σας οδηγήσει στην οδό Ακτή Μουτσοπούλου.. ;) θα βρείτε την διαδρομή στο παρακάτω link:\r\n\r\nhttp://www.google.ro/maps/dir/Platia+Omonias,+Athina,+Greece/Akti+Moutsopoulou+72,+Pireas+185+36,+Greece/@37.9564067,23.6873316,13z/data=!4m14!4m13!1m5!1m1!1s0x14a1bd3003f51083:0xf974302b6c4fb335!2m2!1d23.7281172!2d37.9844383!1m5!1m1!1s0x14a1bbe102ea526d:0xcc6af1e76b13b69d!2m2!1d23.6475822!2d37.9337925!3e0?hl=en\r\n\r\nVIVIR LA VIDA", start_time: "2015-09-18 08:00:00", end_time: nil, eid: "1647867565457562", picture: "https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xpf1/v/t1.0-9/s720x720/11918955_10206987558822927_5784043042157858260_n.jpg?oh=c421d07e929af211ce047f8287af2329&oe=5667A99C", image: "11918955_10206987558822927_5784043042157858260_n.jpg", venue: "", location: "Bayway Cafe Restaurant Club", city: "Athens", country: "", country_code: "GR", longitude: "23.64747855777", latitude: "37.933086854061", website: "", sandbox: true, timezone: nil, slug: "vivir-la-vida-bayway", event_type_id: nil, owner_fb_id: "10206690478516105", sale_notification_email: nil},
  {name: "PARIS FRIDAY'S KIZOMBA NIGHT", description: "Suivez nous / follow us..;) :\r\n\r\nNotre Page FB >> https://www.facebook.com/kizombakhaosuayparis\r\n\r\n\r\n  ★☆ ★ PARIS FRIDAY'S KIZOMBA NIGHT ★☆ ★\r\n\r\n\r\nVENDREDI 18 SEPTEMBRE 2015, Henri et la KRAZZY TEAM vous propose LA soirée KIZOMBA : 20H00 - 05H00..;)\r\n\r\n------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n ★☆ DRESS CODE: BLUE JEAN & WHITE..:)\r\n\r\n♥♥♥ COURS DE KIZOMBA AVEC ALEX & DEDE....;)\r\n\r\n- 20h00 a 21h00 : Débutant\r\n- 21h00 a 22h00 : Intermédiaire\r\n\r\n\r\n♫ ♬ ♫ ♬ AUX PLATINES: DJ JO & DJ ZEN\r\n\r\n- 22h00 à 05h00 : soirée KIZOMBA & SEMBA jusqu'à 5h du matin\r\n\r\nL'équipe des taxi-danseurs pour vous Mesdames et Messieurs (signe distinctif : Ils ONT DES BRACELETS FLUO...:)\r\n\r\nEt toujours à disposition, des petites douceurs (bonbons et fruits frais) pour se ravitailler entre les danses pour les personnes qui viennent tôt..:)\r\n\r\n\r\n> ♥ RDV VENDREDI À 20H AU KHAO SUAY !!!\r\n\r\nTarif :\r\n* 10€ avec SOFT  \r\n* 12€ avec ALCOOL\r\n\r\nEt 2 euros par article pour les vestiaires (obligatoire) .\r\n\r\nCB acceptée...;)\r\n\r\nLES EVENEMENTS ET PHOTOS DE SOIRÉES DU KHAO SUAY SONT PUBLIÉES SUR CE GROUPE!!! \r\nSUIVEZ NOUS / FOLLOW US...;)\r\n>>> https://www.facebook.com/groups/1476037159278488/\r\n____________________________\r\nKHAO SUAY CLUB\r\n20 rue de Lappe 75011 Paris\r\n\r\nTél.: 0677268877\r\n\r\nFB: henri khao suay\r\nwww.khao-suay.com", start_time: "2015-09-18 18:00:00", end_time: "2015-12-26 04:00:00", eid: "956956904325668", picture: "https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xfp1/v/t1.0-9/s720x720/11990413_1005159062874350_7839629125904347257_n.jpg?oh=42ad8c0eb3bc85ef6dca13b4501adea8&oe=566D0036", image: "11990413_1005159062874350_7839629125904347257_n.jpg", venue: "", location: "KHAO SUAY", city: "Paris", country: nil, country_code: "FR", longitude: "2.37252", latitude: "48.8537483", website: "", sandbox: true, timezone: nil, slug: "vendredi-18-